nnoremap c :call SideComment()<CR>a
inoremap c <ESC>:call SideComment()<CR>a
function! SideComment()
    normal 45|
    "don't put space after "
    exe ":normal i" . g:Comment
    "exe ":normal i" . g:Comment . "\ "
endfunction

